name: Small Spiral Earrings - A Rainbow of Colors to Choose From!
description:
Simply sweet little spiral earrings made from permanently-colored copper wire.

Size is approximately 1 inch from top to bottom.

Your earrings will come with rubber stoppers to keep your earrings secure.

Your jewelry arrives on my signature Bohemian Bear jewelry cards ready for gift-giving (or self indulgence!)

This listing is for one pair of earrings. Please include your choice of color--if no choice is given I will choose a color for you.

name: Custom Quote Earrings & Necklace
description:
Custom Quote, Personalized Earrings and Necklace Set

Earrings & Necklace set -- Don't Blink is shown, but this listing is for a custom quote. You choose the quote, and I'll personalize your jewelry for you.

Black with white text so they'll match anything!

My charms are completely designed and created by yours truly! I print my images so they are double-sided and then seal them in crystal clear plastic.

Each charm is about an inch tall. (depending on the size of the quote)

Silver base metal flat French ear wires. (gold colored wires available upon request)

Your earrings will come with rubber stoppers to keep your earrings secure.

Pendant comes on 20 inch stretch cord (you can tie it in a knot to your desired length)

Packaged on my signature BohoBear jewelry cards, ready for gift-giving (or well-deserved self indulgence!)

Water resistant design, but do not wear in water.

name: Dinosaur Skeleton Specimen Jar Necklace
description:
Dinosaur Skeleton Specimen Jar Necklace

Rawr! This is a one of a kind hand drawn, hand made necklace. The jar is hand drawn on lightweight, crystal-clear 5mm plastic with a vintage image of a dino skeleton sealed inside. Your necklace will come with a silver or black 18" stretch cord. Let me know your choice of color. 

Choose T-Rex, T-Rex Skull, or Velociraptor!

All my jewelry comes on my Bohemian Bear jewelry cards, ready for gift giving!

Size: smaller than 2 in. x 2 in.
Small parts: not for children

Thanks for buying handmade!
